{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "两位契约者 第22章 4-3 潜伏之人",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "一行人得知控制塞西娅的并非巴哈姆特，\\n而是连巴哈姆特都能操控的“某人”。\\n为了断绝“某人”对此的掌控，\\n王子一行和奈迪犹合力挑战巴哈姆特。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这里就是塞西娅的精神世界……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "哇！好漂亮的花田！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我看到的是庄严的神殿……\\n我记得这里也会\\n照出自身的意识对吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "没错，你们看到的\\n是你们自身对塞西娅的印象。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "又是美丽的风景又是庄严的建筑，\\n原来大家心里的塞西娅\\n是这样的形象啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "不愧是塞西娅！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "感、感觉有点不好意思呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "咦？塞西娅，你的样貌……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "嗯……看来这里没法\\n使用巴哈姆特的力量呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "你呢，奈迪犹？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "虽说我似乎还能够使用\\n巴哈姆特的力量……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "这个世界里有\\n巴哈姆特的意识的实体，\\n还是不要轻易龙化比较好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴哈姆特",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "巴哈姆特的意识出现了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "过来了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "巴哈姆特！我有话要对你说！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴哈姆特",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "不予理睬吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "你还是不肯接受和我的契约吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "巴哈姆特所寻求的原本就是\\n能使其现身于世的容器。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "所以巴哈姆特最开始的目的\\n就是控制你，\\n也就谈不上什么接受不接受。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "你说的也许没错……\\n可是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "直到刚才为止，\\n我都能感受到巴哈姆特\\n接受了与我的契约。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "可是，巴哈姆特却像突然间\\n发狂了一样……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴哈姆特",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "这确实值得深思，\\n但现在我们似乎\\n没有时间悠闲分析了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "确实……\\n现在只有用武力制服巴哈姆特，\\n让对方明白你不会屈服。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "好的……\\n如果说别无他法……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "那就让我向你证明我的实力吧！\\n巴哈姆特！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01",
                "100039_01",
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "哈啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴哈姆特",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "如此猛烈的攻击\\n也无法让巴哈姆特屈服吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "果然只靠硬碰硬还是不行吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴哈姆特",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯？怎么回事？\\n总觉得有些奇怪……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "尤蒂尔？\\n怎么了？哪里奇怪？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "可能只是我的错觉……\\n巴哈姆特好像很痛苦……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "啊！哥哥也这么觉得吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我来到这个世界后也一直……\\n不，就连我在现实世界中\\n被控制的时候也感觉到了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "巴哈姆特好像很痛苦……\\n就像被操控了一样……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "被操控吗……\\n也许这么说也对……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "奈迪犹，你知道些什么吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "契约虽然分成了两半，\\n但与你我分别缔结契约的\\n巴哈姆特却是同一个。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "然而，我却无法感知\\n这个巴哈姆特的意识。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "也就是说……难道……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "嗯，可以认为是\\n另有他人的意识介入其中。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "很有可能想要控制塞西娅的\\n并不是巴哈姆特，\\n而是潜伏在其身后的“某人”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "也就是说……巴哈姆特真的\\n被什么人给操控了吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01",
                "100009_01",
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "可是这真的有可能吗……\\n究竟是谁才能够操控\\n身为创世之龙的巴哈姆特啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我也没有可靠的证据。\\n但只有这样才能说得通\\n我和塞西娅所感受到的违和感。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "如果你说的是事实，\\n我们有什么解决办法吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我倒是有一个办法，\\n其中最关键的是……\\n尤蒂尔，是你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我！？我究竟能做什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "你似乎对人与龙之间的感应\\n以及魔力的流动很敏感。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "恐怕“某人”正是利用了\\n塞西娅和巴哈姆特的契约\\n而在暗处操控了塞西娅。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "所以，需要你来找出\\n隐藏在契约中的异物，\\n如果可能的话，将其消灭。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这……我能明白塞西娅和巴哈姆特\\n是通过契约连接在一起的。\\n但要从中找出异物这种事……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "当然，也不是让你毫无头绪地找。\\n我这就让那家伙露出马脚。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "露出马脚！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "接下来会让塞西娅来\\n尝试龙化成巴哈姆特。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "诶！？可、可是她一旦龙化的话\\n就会……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "不用完成龙化的整个过程，\\n只要她试图龙化，\\n应该就能激活魔力的流动。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "这时出现在连接塞西娅和巴哈姆特\\n之间的魔力以外的“异物”，\\n一定就是我们要找的东西了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "找出来之后，你就亲自将其斩断。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好的……我试试看。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "……\\n奈迪犹，谢谢你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "嗯？谢我什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_08_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
